{{see|Joke}}
==English==
===Etymology===
from {{L.}} [[iocus]].
===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# an amusing story
# something said or done for amusement
# {{figurative}} a [[worthless]] thing or person
#:''Your effort at cleaning your room is a '''joke'''.''
#:''The president is a '''joke'''.''

